From the problem data:
- Initial "Total Current Assets" value (on 2023-12-31) is 8,000,000.00
- End "Total Current Assets" value (on 2024-02-03) is 9,122,854.19

These are the values representing assets expected to be realised or consumed in the normal operating cycle.
